rtical-align: inherit;">just a matter of representing the data as a polynom=
ial</font></font></strong><font dir=3D"auto" style=3D"vertical-align: inher=
it;"><font dir=3D"auto" style=3D"vertical-align: inherit;"> .</font></font>=
</p>



